<html><head><title>Monster Mission Shards</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>Monster Mission Shards</h3><p>Now that the monster missions require all group members to loot a shard to get experience, there has been some question about where the shards might be found.  Rashere posted today on EQLive, "The shards can come from anything in the mission, but in general you will find them in the same place as the artifact loot."</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Wednesday, 7 December, 2005<br>Link: <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=13253">http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=13253</a><br>Printed On: Mon May 15 15:25:25 PDT 2006<br>©2005 IGN Entertainment</font></span>